  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Beginning at 13th Level, you have truly planned for just about every eventual outcome. </p><p>While you are conscious, you and allied creatures within 30 feet of you cannot be surprised and hostile creatures cannot gain advantage against you or allied creatures within 30 feet of you as a result of being hidden. </p><p>Finally, creatures attacks that would target you cannot benefit from a bonus to hit as the result of a Jutsu. (Such as Advantage or any flat +X based bonus)</p>",
